{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/scrollbar-vertical-macos/","webpackCompilationHash":"268c83d00b7783163f58","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Acabo de toparme con el problema de que macOS oculta las barras de desplazamiento mientras no están en uso, pero la cuestión es que a veces las personas no pueden ver si un div tiene o no una función de desplazamiento.</p>\n<h2 id=\"la-solucion\"><a href=\"#la-solucion\" aria-label=\"la solucion permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>La solución</h2>\n<p>Incluye esto en tu CSS:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">::-webkit-scrollbar</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-appearance</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 7px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 4px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 0 1px <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Puedes personalizar la apariencia si lo necesitas.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Fuente: <a href=\"http://simurai.com/blog/2011/07/26/webkit-scrollbar\">Force the scrollbar back</a></p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Acabo de toparme con el problema de que macOS oculta las barras de desplazamiento mientras no están en uso, pero la cuestión es que a veces…","frontmatter":{"title":"Mostrar el scrollbar vertical en macOS","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":150,"height":150,"src":"/static/695197f9845f4e2da7a3da0e77e784f4/4148e/css.png","srcSet":"/static/695197f9845f4e2da7a3da0e77e784f4/4148e/css.png 1x"}}},"banner":null,"slug":"scrollbar-vertical-macos","date":"2018-06-04T00:00:00.000Z","categories":["Code"],"tags":["css","webkit","macOS"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/scrollbar-vertical-macos/","date":"2018-06-04T00:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/scrollbar-vertical-macos/"}}}